                     <interp inst="t17840526-43-person476" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I found this kettle in the prisoner's hand, full of saloop and fire under it, I am sure it was the prisoner.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840526-43-person477">
                  GEORGE
                   WADE
