                     <interp inst="t17840526-43-person477" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was with the last witness, I took the prisoner, he had the kettle in his hand.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I picked up the kettle full of fire.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840526-43-verdict208" type="verdictDescription">
